=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Feb 25, 2026</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104pym1665702536682.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/pym1665702536682.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/pym1665702536682.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"pym1665702536682\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Restores the initial value of the specified property.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"pym1665702536682__topic_d127718e1_d127719e1_d127720e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"pym1665702536682__p_d127721e1_d127722e1_d127723e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Object</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">.<span class=\"keyword apiname\">clearProperty</span> (</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">PropertyName</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"pym1665702536682__section_w1800ab1b5b3_w1801ab1b5_w1802ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d862714e70\">Arguments </h2>\n<dl class=\"dl parml\" id=\"pym1665702536682__parml_mcq_tg3_dwb\">\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\">PropertyName</dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Name of the property to remove.</dd>\n</dl>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"pym1665702536682__section_w1803ab1b5b5_w1804ab1b5_w1805ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d862714e88\">Exceptions</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The following exceptions may be thrown:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">uniface.InvalidDataObjectException</code></li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"pym1665702536682__section_w1806ab1b5b7_w1807ab1b5_w1808ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d862714e105\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"pym1665702536682__p_d127739e1_d127740e1_d127741e1\">The initial values of the widget properties of a\n        component, entity, occurrence, or field can be set declaratively in the Properties\n        Inspector, and procedurally in ProcScript using the following commands:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"pym1665702536682__ul_s4k_wg3_dwb\">\n<li class=\"li\">For components: <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$componentproperties</span> and\n            <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$instanceproperties</span>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"pym1665702536682__li_d46319e1_d46320e1_d46321e1\">For entities: <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$entityproperties</span>\n          and <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$curentproperties</span>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"pym1665702536682__li_d46322e1_d46323e1_d46324e1\">For occurrences: <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$occproperties</span>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"pym1665702536682__li_d46325e1_d46326e1_d46327e1\">For fields: <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$properties</span> and\n            <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fieldproperties</span>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"pym1665702536682__p_d127742e1_d127743e1_d127744e1\">Once the DSP is loaded, the values of these properties\n        can be dynamically changed in the browser using the <span class=\"keyword apiname\">setProperty</span> and\n          <span class=\"keyword apiname\">setProperties</span> API functions.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"pym1665702536682__p_d127745e1_d127746e1_d127747e1\">You can use the <span class=\"keyword apiname\">clearProperties</span>\n        function to reset all the widget properties of the object to their initial values.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/shk1665703139073.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uniface.InvalidDataObjectException</a><p>Exception thrown if the object on which the function is called is no longer valid.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/sno1665702583691.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Widgets for Dynamic Server Pages</a><p>Widget definitions for Dynamic Server Pages (DSPs) are used to generate the HTML elements and controls used to represent fields, labels, occurrences, and entities displayed in the client browser.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fql1665702536920.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>clearProperties()</a><p>Restores the initial widget properties of the Uniface data object.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hwh1665702536527.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>getProperty()</a><p>Returns the value of a property of this Uniface data object.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nkl1665702536608.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>setProperty()</a><p>Sets the specified widget property to a given value.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/reb1665702537007.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uniface.Entity</a><p>The uniface.Entity object provides access to selected properties of the component entity that it represents. It is returned by the getEntities and getEntity functions of the uniface.Instance and uniface.Occurrence objects.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hfh1665702535808.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uniface.Occurrence</a><p>The uniface.Occurrence object provides access to selected properties of the occurrence that it represents. It is returned by the getOccurrence function of the uniface.Entity object.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dlx1665702535259.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uniface.Field</a><p>The uniface.Field object provides access to selected properties of the field that it represents. It is returned by the getField function of uniface.Occurrence.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mvn1752068459777.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$componentproperties</a><p>Return or set the definition-time widget properties of the current component instance.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/afr1752069080308.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$instanceproperties</a><p>Return or set the current runtime widget properties of current instance.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531140\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531140\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "clearProperty() Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Feb 25, 2026 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Restores the initial value of the specified property. Object . clearProperty ( PropertyName ) Arguments PropertyName Name of the property to remove. Exceptions The following exceptions may be thrown: uniface.InvalidDataObjectException Description The initial values of the widget properties of a component, entity, occurrence, or field can be set declaratively in the Properties Inspector, and procedurally in ProcScript using the following commands: For components: $componentproperties and $instanceproperties For entities: $entityproperties and $curentproperties For occurrences: $occproperties For fields: $properties and $fieldproperties Once the DSP is loaded, the values of these properties can be dynamically changed in the browser using the setProperty and setProperties API functions. You can use the clearProperties function to reset all the widget properties of the object to their initial values. Related Links uniface.InvalidDataObjectException Exception thrown if the object on which the function is called is no longer valid. Widgets for Dynamic Server Pages Widget definitions for Dynamic Server Pages (DSPs) are used to generate the HTML elements and controls used to represent fields, labels, occurrences, and entities displayed in the client browser. clearProperties() Restores the initial widget properties of the Uniface data object. getProperty() Returns the value of a property of this Uniface data object. setProperty() Sets the specified widget property to a given value. uniface.Entity The uniface.Entity object provides access to selected properties of the component entity that it represents. It is returned by the getEntities and getEntity functions of the uniface.Instance and uniface.Occurrence objects. uniface.Occurrence The uniface.Occurrence object provides access to selected properties of the occurrence that it represents. It is returned by the getOccurrence function of the uniface.Entity object. uniface.Field The uniface.Field object provides access to selected properties of the field that it represents. It is returned by the getField function of uniface.Occurrence. $componentproperties Return or set the definition-time widget properties of the current component instance. $instanceproperties Return or set the current runtime widget properties of current instance. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}